{
    "name": "Pediatric Diabetes and Metabolic Precursors",
    "description": "Comprehensive concept set for pediatric diabetes mellitus including Type 1, Type 2, MODY, neonatal diabetes, cystic fibrosis-related diabetes, and all diabetic complications. Also includes metabolic precursors: prediabetes, impaired glucose tolerance, impaired fasting glycemia, hyperglycemia, insulin resistance, and metabolic syndrome. Excludes gestational diabetes mellitus. Designed for use in pediatric (age 2-17) cohort definitions per ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes.",
